title: Play Urban Cafe at White Oaks
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Has an extensive vegan menu with items such as bean bites, veggie chili, quinoa salad, vegan chicken fingers, grilled vegetable sandwich, vegan philly cheesesteak sandwich, sweet potato black bean burger, kale caeser salad. Has Daiya cheese and several vegan faux meats. Located at White Oaks Resort and Spa - a hotel, spa, and fitness club. Note from HappyCow: Please note that the other restaurant (LIV) serves forbidden meats.
